summary: my prediction about detective pikachu: it’s gonna be full of cool moments a ton of on-point pokemon fanservice, but most of the...
body:
my prediction about detective pikachu:

it’s gonna be full of cool moments a ton of on-point pokemon fanservice, but most of the gags are gonna be for very small children. like, there’s gonna be a handful of genuine laughs, sure, but most of the gags are gonna be aimed towards kids.
